    "en": {
      "title": "Playing an air force corporal is the corporal himself",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Air Force has clarified the facts regarding the news on social media that 'an Air Force soldier is kidnapped and attacked by an unknown group'.",
        "Corporal P. Air force member Ratnasooriya was tied to a tree yesterday (28th) morning and was taken to the hospital after local residents informed Valachchena police.",
        "The police have also found a sign near the tree which says, \"This is how people who help brutal politics are put to death\" in Tamil.",
        "However, in an investigation by Valachchena police, it has been revealed that he has done all these actions himself."
      ],
